\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下巴得啲細毛<br />\n上唇一個禮拜唔剃都唔會生密哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唇果d唔長唔短成個大陸仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好想留"},{"pid":"9292d93242925085909f5900bcbf4f6f52c32488","tid":38340,"uid":24755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生得好撚慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d朋友一日唔剃鬍生出黎既量多過我留兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇方法生得多d</blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下巴得啲細毛<br />\n上唇一個禮拜唔剃都唔會生密哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唇果d唔長唔短成個大陸仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好想留</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾大, 我廿歲個陣已經成面鬚好密"},{"pid":"84670d764d6d982bf0451a33ee7aaddef037a529","tid":38340,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"唉 19歲好少鬚<br />\n我都想成面都係呀<br />\n可以留 可以唔留"},{"pid":"1c7368c49603cc049a81dfdf3993c6c92231641d","tid":38340,"uid":39729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"有啲朋友差唔多30都冇乜鬚, 而我就好剔極都唔會淨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下晝已經好似長返. btw想問下各位用剃鬚刀定機多, 就算我用刀都係剃唔淨, 會唔會用機仲方便.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd6cd26efc73eb4feabf3e9063d39eb86f2fdc6","tid":38340,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:12:59.000Z","msg":"兩日要剃一次<br />\n但尋晚剃 聽日晏晝已經出根<br />\n仲要成撚日剃損<br />\n咩角度咩力度都會界一界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人話我知點解會剃極都損一次<br />\n有用爽膚水 用剃刀同剃鬚刀"},{"pid":"f6ac66524644e2140ea66de351394011c10dd9c0","tid":38340,"uid":4867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲朋友差唔多30都冇乜鬚, 而我就好剔極都唔會淨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下晝已經好似長返. btw想問下各位用剃鬚刀定機多, 就算我用刀都係剃唔淨, 會唔會用機仲方便.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用機我果隻唔知點解成日有幾條死剩種起度"},{"pid":"4370d212b01c998d49089f918dc1bebfd8dad125","tid":38340,"uid":39729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有啲朋友差唔多30都冇乜鬚, 而我就好剔極都唔會淨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下晝已經好似長返. btw想問下各位用剃鬚刀定機多, 就算我用刀都係剃唔淨, 會唔會用機仲方便.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用機我果隻唔知點解成日有幾條死剩種起度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機冇研究, 千機銀一部唔捨得買, 睇下其他巴打見解. 機淨係細個用過, 好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 唔知依家啲高級嘢會唔會好啲"},{"pid":"6cc56679dc578c133d44db10ab5fb91af9e8a834","tid":38340,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"好想做鬍鬚佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但啲鬚生得慢又疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8328035f890ae5ede5987d65126d9d97ad21874e","tid":38340,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下巴得啲細毛<br />\n上唇一個禮拜唔剃都唔會生密哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唇果d唔長唔短成個大陸仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好想留</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打幾大, 我廿歲個陣已經成面鬚好密</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n25啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的水對落都有d毛仔 似係會成面鬚果類<br />\n但宜家d鬚生得勁慢"},{"pid":"10999b80aa1ccddada19fd5381c9e396aef07b54","tid":38340,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0